Goenchem Prochar Madheom

Goem, ek lhan (3,700 chovkott kilometr, 1.4 milianv lokvosti)
adli Purtugez vosnnuk ani sod'deak Bharotantli dhaktto prant
zo dokxinn Asiechea ostompt doriadeger urta. Tachem prochar
madheom khoreponni guspagondollachem jem somzunk avgodd ani
zacher zaitem uloilolem melltta.

==Fattbhuim==

Vorsam modem prochar madheomant, zaito bodol
zalolo dista (adlea 20vea xekddeachea disanim) jen'na tem
Katolk somazant probhavi pongddachem zhuzamoll aslem (zati
mandpi xikloleancho vo vegllea rajki vibhaglolea pongddancho
aspav asun) zoim probhavi ani xiklolea ganvkaranim xek
choloilo. 1961 vorsa, Purtugez razvottke uprant,zaitim
vortomanpotram suru kelint jim ganvchea probhavi minachea
pongddanchim aslim. Henvuim, halim bodol'lam ani kaim prochar
madheom rajki pokxank lagim ailam.

==Inglix ani Moratthi==

Chodd vachlolim Goenchim vortomanpotram
Inglix ani Moratthi bhaxent asat ani chodd uloilole thollavea
Konknni bhaxent ekuch Sunaparant nanvachem disallem
asa.Hachem karonn, Moratthi ani Inglix chodd sahitik ani
borovpachea gorzank Goeant sod'deak vapuddttat ani Konknni
chodd uloiloli bhas urta.Ek motint dhorpachi gozal mhonnche
Konknni virudh Moratthi bhaxechea zhogddeank lagun don
bhasanchea zomeam modem dusmankai zanvk pavlea (2006 vorsant,

Konknnichea Devnagri lipi ani Romi lipi vapuddpeam modem
kizil cholta).

Inglix bhaxentlim Goenchim disallim The Navhind Times jem
Dempo minachi komponi 1963 thavn uzvaddaita ani sod'deak
(Febrer 2006) Arun Sinha sompadaita, adlem Purtugez
bhaxentlem disallem atam Inglix bhaxentlea vhodd akarachem
Herald nanvanchem vo chodd nondnikoronn kel'lea nanvan O
Heraldo mhonn vollkhotat zacho dhoni Fernandes Publications
zavn asa zo pongodd chhap'pachea ud'degant aslo zo adlea
tanchea pustok mandda vorvim vaddunk pavla. Tisrem, Inglix
bhaxentlem dispotr The Gomantak Times zachem dhoniponn
Chowgule mina kompone koddlean rajki sombond aslolea
sezarchea Mharaxttr prantantlea Pawar kuttumba kodden gelam.

Febrer 2006,Herald ani Gomantak Times hanche sompadpi Robin
Abreu Mumboicho adlo potrkar ani Sanjay Gupta adim
Kolkatachea The Telegraph hantunt ani her potranim vavurpi
zavn asat.

Ekmev Inglix mhoineallem Goa Today,Vinayak Naik sompadaita
ani Goa Publications tacho dhoni,jem Sallganvkar mina komponi
choloita. Her porgottneo Inglix bhaxentleo Goa Messenger,Goan
Observer, adi zavn asat.

Moratthi molleant, nanvlovkik potram Tarun Bharot (jem adim
sezarchea Belganv xarant thavn porgott zatalem punn atam
Porvori tancho chhapkhanno asa); Gomantak( Gomantak Times
hachem sangati ani adlem probhavik); Navhind Times hachem
Navprabha/Dempo gottachem ani her porgottneo choddxeo
'Goencheo avruti' uzvaddavop jim Goeam bhair thavn chhaptat
ani zancheo kocheri Goenchea bhair asat.

Novi ghoddnni Gova Dhoot uzvaddavop jem adlea raj korpi
Bharotia Janta Pokx hankam lagim asa punn survat korpi hem
nakartat. Anik tin doskanchem adlem vortomanpotr, Moratthi
disallem Raxttrmot Dokxinn Goenchea Moddganv xarantlem jem
hea doskacheam survatek bond poddlem.

1980 vorsa, Romi Konknnint Novem Goem duddvanche oddchonnek
ani goir karbharak lagun bond poddlem. Tachi survat vhodde
umedin ani Goenchi podiatra korun duddu ektthavn kel'li.

==Akaxvanni==

Emissora de Goa, ek bollixtt reddio sttexon aslem
jem Purtugez kallar khub lok umedin aikotalo. Tacho sttudio
Goenchea rajdhani Ponnjechea voir Altinho dongurler asa punn
tacho ttransmittor 5 kilometr ontracher Bambole urta. Bambole
bollixtt ttransmittor asa zo Bharotachea ontoraxttrik
kariakromant, porki bhasancheo kariavolli vitraita.

