==Vitravnechi fattbhuim==

Modlea nnovodant, jen'na Bharotant
poilo khasgi FM vitravnnecho proiog kelo, ten'na Goem- hem
dhakttea bhonvddekaranchem pennem, desachea panchvea zagear
urlem zoim khasgi ud'degkarank FMchi suvat mell'lli.Her chear
kendram, motthim mhanogram zoxem Delhi, Mumboi, Kolkatra ani
Chennai aslim.

Dusrea panvddeachem FM porvangek,Goem (chodd korun rajdhani
Ponnji) zoim lokvosti ek lak tem tin lak asa dekhun 'D'
vorgachea xarant vibhaglem.

Khasgi FM 'D' vorg xarantleanim ek tem tin KW ERP
(ttransmittor utponachem boll) vapddum ieta. (Hi xaranchi
vibhagnni lokvosteche ghottaiecher adarleli asa. Dekhik,
Kolkata A+ xarak ,Chandigodd chea 'C' vorgachea xara von unno
lans mell'llo. Bharotacheo FM dusrea panvdeachea dhornnachem
mahitipotr www.mib.nic.in hanga pollonvk melltta).

Goem, ho Bharotacho dhaktto prant zachi 1.4 milianv lokvosti
asa thoim zoitivont lans ghevpi oxe asle: ENIL (Times
pongodd-Radio Mirchi) 17.1 milianv Rupia; Indigo (BPL-Rajiv
Chandrashekar) 12.9 milianv Rupia; ani Adlabs
(Reliance-Ambani pongodd) 12.1 milianv Rupia.

Bharotachem sod'deachem dhoronn, dha vorsanchea porvange
kallak ek pavttechi chiptti formaita. (Bharoti hixeobache
chalint, ho duddvam ankddo dha vorsank dor vorsak 10
ttoke.Dusrea utramnim, komponechea faido-luskonn hixeobant
ENIL tanche 17.1 milianv Rupia, dor vorsak 1.71 milianv Rupia
hixeobant dhortoli.

Sogleant unni voidh lansachi rakhiv kimot 25 ttokeancher
ankhnni kelea. Hea babtint. Goenchea bhanddvollachi rakhiv
kimot 4.27 milianv Rupia asa.

Vorsuki porvange chiptti khasgi komponeank mhosulache 4 ttoke
vo rakhiv kimoteche 10 ttoke, khoinchem chodd tem, tharailea.
Tea pasvot, unneant unnem khatrechem vorsachem bhorop Ponnji
FM choloitoleank 4.27 milianv Rupiache 10 ttoke vo 427000
Rupia (mhosul chodd aslea kheriz).

Poilim, Bharotachem proitn FM khasgikoronn korpak borem
cholunk na jen'na khasgi komponeank koblati pormonnem
sorkarak ievjilolea pormonnem duddu zoma korunk ghoddlem na.
Poilea panvddeache FM (vors 2000) choddant chodd pavnnecho
lans Goeant 41.5 milianv Rupia aslo. Tea dhoronna promonnem,
hachi vadd zavn- dor vorsa 15 ttoke- 146 milianv Rupiancher
10vea vorsa pavta asli.Lans ghevpeank 42.6 kotti rupia 10
vorsam modem bhorunk poddtta asle.Mottheo komponeo fattim
sorleo dekhun thoddeank ojeap disunkna.

Hea vellar ekuch thollavi Goenchi komponi porvangi magunk
lans divpi Tarun Bharat Multigraphics zavn asli. Punn lans
jikhpi sogleo komponeo Goeam bhaileo asun, hacho vahinicher
koslo porinnam zatolo tem pollonvchem asa.

Soglea tin zoitivont lans divpeank ttransmittor mull sovloti,
dhoronnant bodol korna zalear, Akaxvannichea sangata Ponnje
lagsor tharavcheo poddttoleo.

Akaxvannichea FM Rainbow haka 6 KW ttransmittor asa ani ho
Goenchea pois zageancher aikunk iena. Khasgi FM cholovpeank 3
KW tankichea ttransmittorank maniotai dilea.

Radio Mirchi (Times FM pongddantlo, ek Bharoti motthea
vortomanpotr sankllecho) zaitea kalla uprant Goeant portun
ieta. 1980 vorsa xevottak ani 1990 chea survatek Times FM
Ponnjechea Akaxvanni FM vahinintlo vitravnnecho vell vikto
ghetalem.

Tin nove 24 horanche stereo vahini 2006 xevttak suru zanvche
asat. Times poilo asot, punn herui astolet.

C ani D vorgachea xarank, zalleant ani kariavollinchea
bhagidarint maniotai dilea punn vahineo apleo ghorcheo
kariavolli korunk posont kortat.

Khasgi FM hankam khobrank porvangi na (zorui lagu zavpi
montri don tin vorsanim fer vichar korit). Raxttrik
patlicher,sod'deacheo FM komponio- zoxeo Times of
India,Hindustan Times, Mid-Day, BBC, adi- chodd korun
vortoman potrancheo sanklli vo prochar madheom, FM hacher
khobram khatir chodd zor ditat.

