==Prochar madheomacho odmas==

1980 chea survatek boroitana,
manovxastri Dr Robert S Newman aplea borovpant Goenchea
prochar madheomachi "motthea kuttumbaxim" sombond
dakhoita.Hantunt hatbhor dhaktte ud'degkar, paromporik
bhattkar ani zhuzantle faidekar zankam min kaddpachi porvangi
mell'li ani tem min Japanank patthovpak dilem (dusrem
sonvsari zhuz zalea uprant porot bandhnne khatir) hancho
aspav asa.

Goa- The Transformation of an Indian Region, Pacific Affairs
(August 1984) hantunt Newman hannim Goencher ek nibond
boroila: "(vosnnuk rajea uprantlo Goencho Mukhel Montri
Dayanand)" Bandodkar ani tache sangati karkhandaranim
porjechem mot aplea potram ani tanchea tisrea panvddeachea
xikxonn sounsthani jim tanninch sthaplolim udexim akarunk
proitn kele( ekui svotont potr Goeant na). Dekhik Chowgule
komponen Gomantak ani Uzvadd vortomanpotram suru kelint ani
Moddganv kola ani vineanche kolejiche te provortok asle,
Sallganvkaran kaidea kolej sthapli, Dempo The Navhind Times
ani Navprabha-che dhoni je Miramarchea Dhempe kolejint
ghuspolole asat. 

Anik ek nibond Popular Protest and the Free Goa Press (91-113
panam) hantunt Norman Dantas aplea The Transformationof Goa
(The other India Press, Mapusa, 1999) hantunt oxi cheorchea
korta: Goeant, dispotrachea ogrlekhanim nixedh chollvollim
voir, ek boreponnachi chalnuk dakhoinant ani oslea vixoiacher
nixedhan revoddlole Goenchea pongddank, prochar madheoma
koddlea vaitt onnubhov mell'lla. Nixedh ani prochar
madheomachi ani Goencher tachi vagnnuk tin doskanchea kallant
survat 'satthint tem nnovovdant 'poriant, hem polleta.

